Library Management System
This is a simple command-line application built with Csharp and SQLite for managing a library's book collection. It allows you to perform basic operations like adding, viewing, updating, and removing book records.

Features
Add New Book: Add a new book record with a title and author.

Display All Books: View a list of all books currently in the library, with their unique IDs.

Update Book Record: Update the title and author of a book by its ID.

Remove Book: Delete a book record by its ID.

Input Validation: Ensures that user input for names and IDs is valid.

Technologies Used
Language: C#

Framework: .NET (Console Application)

Database: SQLite

Database Library: Microsoft.Data.Sqlite
